title: Episode 14 Ft. Gunplay
itunes:title: Episode 14 Ft. Gunplay
description:
Gunplay passes through Lip Service and sits down with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Leah McSweeney to discuss why his perfect woman isn't so perfect, if you should hold your man down while he's in jail, and Stephanie admits to her boyfriend she was wrong. Leah gets advice from Gunplay about her new relationship and what she needs that she hasn't gotten...yet!
